# Precious Alloy VMS — Design Phase

While designing this app, work **frontend only**. Do not expand into backend work.

## Hard constraints

- **React UI/UX only** — redesign screens with the new design language; keep functionality the same
- **No new backend fields** — no DocType / Custom Field / schema changes
- **No custom APIs** — use existing Frappe / `react_api` methods only
- Do **not** change ERPNext or Frappe core app code

## Design system (required)

Follow `/DESIGN.md` and `frontend/src/styles/tokens.css`.

- Company: **Precious Alloy Components Pvt. Ltd.**
- Logo: only `BrandLogo` → light/dark wordmark + icon under `public/brand/` (theme-aware)
- Welcome splash is **inside Add Visitor /check-in**, not login
- Feel: premium industrial enterprise (Fluent / Fiori / Honeywell-like) — not startup
- Primary `#0A3D91` · Hover `#0F4FB5` · Dark navy `#14213D` · Bg `#F8FAFC` · Surface white
- Status: Pending amber · Approved green · Checked-in blue · Meeting indigo · Out slate · Rejected red
- No gradients-as-brand, no violet/pink/coral/cream, no glassmorphism
- Poppins 400–700 · Lucide icons stroke 2 · cards 20px · primary buttons 52px / 14px radius
- Gate pass = boarding-pass dark navy card with QR / barcode

## PWA surfaces

Welcome → OTP → Details → Host → Approval → Check-in → Gate pass → Meeting → Checkout  
Ops: Dashboard · Live visitors · Approvals · Reports · Profile

Flow: `Pending → Approved → Check-in → Meeting Done → Check Out`

After frontend changes: `cd frontend && npm run build`.
